  Locus:
    Page: 20
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Anger
---
When you allow thoughts of anger. ...to exercise sway, they have a
corroding and poisoning effect upon the organism; they pull it down, and if
allowed to continue will eventually tear it to pieces by externalizing
themselves in particular forms of disease.
